trans-unit.source: Provides a collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> class is a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects, typically used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object to manage a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects for a connection.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> clase es una colección de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos, que normalmente utilizados el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> objeto para administrar un conjunto de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos para una conexión.

trans-unit.source: The transformers related to a Web Parts connection can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Los convertidores de él relacionadas con una conexión de elementos Web se pueden recuperar mediante el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> to be added to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> que se va a agregar al final de la colección <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds an object to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Agrega un objeto al final de la colección.

trans-unit.source: The index at which <paramref name="transformer" /> has been added.
trans-unit.target: Índice en el que se ha agregado el parámetro <paramref name="transformer" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> que se comprueba para determinar si pertenece a la colección.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether a particular transformer exists in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve un valor que indica si existe un determinado transformador en la colección.

trans-unit.source: A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular transformer is in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Un valor booleano que indica si un determinado transformador pertenece a la colección.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.Contains%2A> method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> object and determine whether it is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.Contains%2A> método le permite comprobar un determinado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objeto y determinar si forma parte de un <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> objeto.

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects to contain the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: Matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> que va a contener la colección copiada.

trans-unit.source: The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
trans-unit.target: Posición inicial de la matriz en la que se va a colocar el contenido de la colección.

trans-unit.source: Copies the collection to an array of <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Copia la colección en una matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.CopyTo%2A> method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> collection, a subset of those objects, or a superset of those objects.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection.CopyTo%2A> método resulta útil cuando desea ensamblar una matriz personalizada que puede contener todos los <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objetos en el <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> colección, un subconjunto de esos objetos o un superconjunto de los objetos.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> that is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> que es miembro de la colección.

trans-unit.source: Returns the position of a particular member in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve la posición de un miembro determinado de la colección.

trans-unit.source: An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Entero que indica la posición de un objeto determinado en la colección.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which a value should be inserted.
trans-unit.target: Índice de base cero en el que se debe insertar un valor.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> to insert.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> que se va a insertar.

trans-unit.source: Inserts a transformer into the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" /> collection at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Inserta un transformador en la colección <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection" />, en el índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si la colección es de solo lectura.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the collection and its items cannot be changed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> si no se puede modificar la colección y sus elementos; de lo contrario, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: The index of a particular <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> in a collection.
trans-unit.target: Índice de un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> determinado de una colección.

trans-unit.source: Returns a member of the collection based on its position in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve un miembro de la colección según su posición en la colección.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> located at <paramref name="index" />.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> localizado en <paramref name="index" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> to remove from the collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer" /> que se va a quitar de la colección.

trans-unit.source: Removes the first occurrence of a specific transformer.
trans-unit.target: Elimina la primera aparición de un transformador específico.
